snippet.title: Freja And The Sequel Trailer
snippet.description:
Freja and the sequel is a (free!) classic point-and-click-adventure and interactive story. It's funny, scary (yes, there a zombies in it!) and surreal. Freja, an aspiring computer game designer, is forced (at gunpoint) to make a sequel to a classic game, and becomes embroiled in a mystery where it's hard to distinguish between imagination, creativity and reality.

Get the game!:
iOS (iPad and IPhone): https://t.co/u8OazIoUgE
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...
Windows, Linux or Mac: http://www.biscuitplacebo.com/freja_a...
